<p>These days we do lots of swiping on our devices, and sometimes the results are expected, other times not so much! Listen as John and Dave share tips and answer questions about swiping. That&#039;s not all, of course, the topics expand from there, including a great dive into USB speeds on Apple&#039;s new iPads. Listen as your two favorite geeks walk through all of this for you this week!</p>
